    "The second reason is cross-modality distillation with the proposed contrastive loss can learn the inner correlations between different modality features.",
    "To evaluate the effectiveness of CKLE under the limited label settings which is a common scenario in the medical application, we conduct the experiments by reducing the ratio of labeled training data on the heart failure prediction.",
